CBRE is delighted to offer 5–7 Alick Road, Tottenham for lease.

The property is positioned in the tightly held inner western industrial hub of Tottenham, where opportunities are often sought and rarely found. 

Situated just off Somerville Road, this property features excellent access to major arterials including the West Gate Freeway, the Princes Freeway and the Western Ring Road. It is approximately 6 km to the Port of Melbourne, 11 km to the CBD and 22 km to Melbourne Airport.

Property features include: 
+ Corner site with multiple roller door access points
+ Ability to drive through the facility 
+ Large existing power supply
+ Generous staff amenities
+ Impressive canopy spanning majority of the yard
+ Two titles, flexible occupation arrangements 
+ Large power supply 
+ Impressive ground floor office 
+ Full staff amenities

Key building areas: 
+ Warehouse area: 2,000sqm* 
+ Office area: 210sqm* 
+ Canopy: 530sqm* 
+ Cool room: 1,000sqm* 
+ Humidifier rooms: 300sqm* 
+ Yard area: 800sqm* 

The inner west position offers immediate access to Geelong Road and the West Gate freeway via Grieve Parade.

For further information, please contact the CBRE agents. 

*approx.
